The paper focuses on natural language processing and information retrieval, which are core topics in the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The use of deep language models and neural networks also suggests a connection to the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Deep Learning (cs.DL).
